name: PLAY AND FLAY
description:
Story about flying angel that trying to survive from obstacle. We all know that Mount Semeru eruption made a big impact for society around the mountain. Be patient is how to move on from this condition. Like a flying cupid, please try hard to keep moving go out from the barrier. So good luck !

This work is part of a charity to help victims of the natural disaster from Mount Semeru eruption, every sale in the first market will be 100% donated to the victims, through sewon NFT. #tezos4semeru 

.Mp4 1080 x 720
